https://github.com/esp8266/esp8266-wiki/wiki/Boot-Process#esp-boot-modes

 reset causes:
        0:
        1: normal boot
        2: reset pin
        3: software reset
        4: watchdog reset

    boot device:
        0:
        1: ram
        3: flash